                                        <depth unit="cm">9.2</depth>
                                    </dimensions>
                                </support>
                                <condition/>
                            </supportDesc>
                            <layoutDesc>
                                <layout>
                                    <p>Four lines of Latin text, roughly centred on stone (although line 1 is quite crowded, and it is possible that letter is missing at the end of the line). Interpuncts used only in line 1, but they are irregular in shape from each other. There is a large 'G', inscribed in line 4 at the centre of the stone.</p>
                                    <rs ana="#execution.chiselled" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1">chiselled</rs>
