                        <note>Text of autopsy</note>
                    </app>
                    <app loc="line 1">
                        <note>Although Bivona records P(ublius), autopsy of the stone reveals that the stone reads 'T' followed by an interpunct.</note>
                    </app>
                    <app loc="line 1">
                        <note>It is possible, though by no means certain, that one letter is missing at the end of line 1.</note>
